      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COURTHEZON (4) Captivant colt resuming from a lengthy break. Went back from the wide gate and made a little round late when fifth over 1000m at Eagle Farm last October. Looks ready to go with the two trials and returns in a winnable race. LAST TOUR (5) deep into the campaign and never handled the heavy (8) going with a struggling eighth over 1400m at Newcastle. Comes back in trip from the better draw and is expected to go close. PEACE BIRD (1) has her hoof on the till and finds a much weaker contest today with the claim. Sat on the speed and no match for Funshow when second in the small field over 1300m at Newcastle. Stays in the mix. BELLA MANDA (7) two-year-old Trapeze Artist filly from Bella Rossie on debut for the Archibald yard. Primed with the three trials and the blinkers go on from the low draw. Keep safe.",
